Hey,

Here is my new and short mpbhop map. (no fly, I swear)

Bhop_aster

The map is made for legit bhop, and length is about 45 seconds if you don't fail. It's an easy/medium map, everyone should be able to finish it without a lot of troubles.

I kinda mapped everything that goes through my mind, but I like the result, I hope you'll enjoy it.

[FlyBhopper](http://steamcommunity.com/groups/flybhopbest "FlyBhopper")
